content.text:
In *Ware-wolf Campfire Stories*, 5 campers sit around a fire and tell tales.. with consequences.

The game is a compilation made by 15 dev teams from the Playdate Pulp community, released for FREE on Halloween. Each story a camper tells launches a bespoke, spooky experience.

Screenshots of the varied gameplay below and more additional at the QR.
